cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on Named Entity Recognition (NER) on informal text types, specifically microblog texts, for Turkish language. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper utilizes a semi-supervised learning approach based on neural networks for NER. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the paper deals with extracting information from social media, specifically Twitter messages. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper uses word embeddings, which is a popular technique in natural language processing and machine learning. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a possible category as the paper utilizes neural networks for semi-supervised learning.
